{"tid":1096374,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"15歲腎衰竭，心臟病狗狗，血尿","createTime":"2019-04-07T16:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T10:09:15.000Z","uid":130392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ceb1d0d5295d96436c8c991d4321188a693efe30","tid":1096374,"uid":130392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:08:11.000Z","msg":"我狗仔15歲<br />\n腎衰竭，貧血，心臟病<br />\n要每星期打造血針，同定期覆診睇下個腎<br />\n4個月前醫生估佢只有多半年至一年命<br />\n琴日開始痾爛屎同血尿<br />\n即刻帶佢睇醫生<br />\n照左超聲波，驗左血同尿<br />\n醫生只見到膀胱同腎都有石(之前都有，一直用控制緊)<br />\n但醫生話唔肯定確實原因<br />\n因為太多可能性<br />\n要做ct先知<br />\n但ct要全身麻醉，佢有心臟病加勁多病痛<br />\n佢要全身麻醉係好大風險<br />\n到搵到原因，九成九都係要做手術<br />\n佢要捱過手術，更難<br />\n而家唔知點好，做又唔係唔做又唔係<br />\n佢精神同胃口暫時正常<br />\n但岩岩開始勁尿頻，無尿都係咁要痾<br />\n聽日再帶佢去見另一個醫生<br />\n我應該點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd26b95dfeeb31e81effec88e050af23b498241","tid":1096374,"uid":54121,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:10:09.000Z","msg":"安樂死 除非你想睇佢愈來愈痛苦"},{"pid":"7ad76e2403f3b7d13bc85dc1cb6feab11eadc78d","tid":1096374,"uid":1444,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:13:15.000Z","msg":"可唔可以綁住做ct <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d0e54f2a1ae53164e66c00e1f05cde9ef6c3f4","tid":1096374,"uid":148332,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:14:40.000Z","msg":"個人認為唔好check同手術了，手術完都唔會長命左，道理同d阿伯阿婆90幾歲患癌唔會積極治療一樣..."},{"pid":"4e99754ceba2e2fd233909c8b2ddfa273876b0dc","tid":1096374,"uid":235520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"安樂死 <br />\n比佢無痛苦同有尊嚴咁走"},{"pid":"6215732a0b18f1051b0f2eccdc4843ceed3ca522","tid":1096374,"uid":18844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e99754ceba2e2fd233909c8b2ddfa273876b0dc","tid":1096374,"uid":235520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"安樂死 <br />\n比佢無痛苦同有尊嚴咁走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\n好心快啲俾佢走"},{"pid":"16533859242b7c8759ab10979a19357e834b41b6","tid":1096374,"uid":130392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bd26b95dfeeb31e81effec88e050af23b498241","tid":1096374,"uid":54121,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:10:09.000Z","msg":"安樂死 除非你想睇佢愈來愈痛苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:50:36.000Z","msg":"但佢仲行得走得食得精神好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714ce78a5fe50a4d0cbf0f14830527b2c339d834","tid":1096374,"uid":130392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8d0e54f2a1ae53164e66c00e1f05cde9ef6c3f4","tid":1096374,"uid":148332,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:14:40.000Z","msg":"個人認為唔好check同手術了，手術完都唔會長命左，道理同d阿伯阿婆90幾歲患癌唔會積極治療一樣..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:51:37.000Z","msg":"我都唔想手術<br />\n唔想佢咁痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ad18795c970a2448e8fc89d46fd8fd785d8f01","tid":1096374,"uid":130392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e99754ceba2e2fd233909c8b2ddfa273876b0dc","tid":1096374,"uid":235520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"安樂死 <br />\n比佢無痛苦同有尊嚴咁走"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"但呢一刻佢仲行得走得食得精神好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87db566a2c39f33525da68c9237ff0a4dd8c2469","tid":1096374,"uid":141424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:54:29.000Z","msg":"搵第二個醫生 你著鉛衫入去陪佢照<br />\n似有腎石 痾唔出尿<br />\n所以成日想痾"},{"pid":"be790c35e807e41a75cfc8fa7a50e388e52afdfd","tid":1096374,"uid":149063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T17:21:36.000Z","msg":"如果可以，不如你陪佢行埋最後呢段路，有咩想做都陪佢做。行得走得仲肯食野咪當一隻正常既狗仔去養，只不過你需要用多啲時間去照顧佢起居飲食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b87293f59a0bf0fa601d65da82b955e374b1861","tid":1096374,"uid":235520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40ad18795c970a2448e8fc89d46fd8fd785d8f01","tid":1096374,"uid":130392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e99754ceba2e2fd233909c8b2ddfa273876b0dc","tid":1096374,"uid":235520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"安樂死 <br />\n比佢無痛苦同有尊嚴咁走"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"但呢一刻佢仲行得走得食得精神好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T17:47:07.000Z","msg":"聽日你去問左醫生意見先<br />\n如果都係相同答案 <br />\n咁你搵定安樂死公司既資料啦 <br />\n真係要做定功課 到時狗狗有咩特發情況 情況變得好差既話 <br />\n咁真係時候比佢舒服D咁走啦 <br />\n生死有命"},{"pid":"7b850436680a01846520261c34e0badc7b9d0b62","tid":1096374,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T18:24:14.000Z","msg":"好高機會屙爛屎同腎衰竭有關， <br />\n屙爛屎後好快就會抽筋 <br />\n抽筋好辛苦，而且一次比一次嚴重一次比一次頻密<br />\n問吓獸醫意見，獸醫都會建議佢打針，唔好俾佢抽筋 <br />\n首先要搞清楚屙爛屎同腎衰竭有冇關係"},{"pid":"c97d3d2dade914bc563c088e784089fb3366f363","tid":1096374,"uid":130392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b850436680a01846520261c34e0badc7b9d0b62","tid":1096374,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T18:24:14.000Z","msg":"好高機會屙爛屎同腎衰竭有關， <br />\n屙爛屎後好快就會抽筋 <br />\n抽筋好辛苦，而且一次比一次嚴重一次比一次頻密<br />\n問吓獸醫意見，獸醫都會建議佢打針，唔好俾佢抽筋 <br />\n首先要搞清楚屙爛屎同腎衰竭有冇關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:44:33.000Z","msg":"上次個醫生話應該唔關事<br />\n我聽日會再問下<br />\n不過佢今日d便便好d，無咁爛，只係軟d"},{"pid":"52b556380b90810528d4bd5da5d0476a55b7c0d2","tid":1096374,"uid":185498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40ad18795c970a2448e8fc89d46fd8fd785d8f01","tid":1096374,"uid":130392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e99754ceba2e2fd233909c8b2ddfa273876b0dc","tid":1096374,"uid":235520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"安樂死 <br />\n比佢無痛苦同有尊嚴咁走"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"但呢一刻佢仲行得走得食得精神好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"小動物情況可以好短時間內惡化/好轉<br />\n我隻貓女腎病兼貧血，前一晚仲有精神食嘢行嚟行去<br />\n但第二日下午就突然變成又暈又冇精神情況好差<br />\n再第二朝連貓砂盤都冇力上去，就咁尿咗喺砂盤出面<br />\n睇咗兩個醫生都話搵血輸唔係唔可以，但預咗只係買少少時間<br />\n我唔想見到佢辛苦落去，亦覺得係時候所以幫佢決定打針走<br />\n但巴打你要有定心理準備，無論你做咩決定都有機會後悔，你覺得嗰個決定為佢好就足夠"},{"pid":"0952f3d2b30e4f5e8effbdd3a67d156166190d04","tid":1096374,"uid":38033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T20:10:33.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主每月洗費大概幾多？<br />\n因為我都有隻腎衰竭+胰臟炎+腎石+貧血要打造血針既15歲貓<br />\n<br />\n想預計下，因為我都係出黎做野冇耐"},{"pid":"6fc4ab0550c2049ea8c5a828f4b4babaac35d871","tid":1096374,"uid":38033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52b556380b90810528d4bd5da5d0476a55b7c0d2","tid":1096374,"uid":185498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40ad18795c970a2448e8fc89d46fd8fd785d8f01","tid":1096374,"uid":130392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e99754ceba2e2fd233909c8b2ddfa273876b0dc","tid":1096374,"uid":235520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"安樂死 <br />\n比佢無痛苦同有尊嚴咁走"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"但呢一刻佢仲行得走得食得精神好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"小動物情況可以好短時間內惡化/好轉<br />\n我隻貓女腎病兼貧血，前一晚仲有精神食嘢行嚟行去<br />\n但第二日下午就突然變成又暈又冇精神情況好差<br />\n再第二朝連貓砂盤都冇力上去，就咁尿咗喺砂盤出面<br />\n睇咗兩個醫生都話搵血輸唔係唔可以，但預咗只係買少少時間<br />\n我唔想見到佢辛苦落去，亦覺得係時候所以幫佢決定打針走<br />\n但巴打你要有定心理準備，無論你做咩決定都有機會後悔，你覺得嗰個決定為佢好就足夠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T20:11:03.000Z","msg":"睇到就傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d5b7996eec2b51fa51059eb30b07200a651698","tid":1096374,"uid":130392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52b556380b90810528d4bd5da5d0476a55b7c0d2","tid":1096374,"uid":185498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40ad18795c970a2448e8fc89